        <Parent_String>Castile soap [300266181], hard soap [300266180], soap (organic material) [300014329], organic material [300011792], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
